engineCMS::eTemplate()

Description
    public bool engineCMS::eTemplate(string $func, string $value)
    1. Loads file for a given template name.
    2. Includes the header or footer markup stored in a PHP file for a given template.

Parameters
    func
	Either "load" or "include"
    value
	A valid template name

Return Values
    Returns TRUE if the function executes successfully.  Returns FALSE if func or value parameters are invalid.

Examples
    
    Example #1
	<?php
	    ...
            $engine->eTemplate("load","systems");
	    ...
	?>

    Example #2
	<?php
	    ...
	    $engine->eTemplate("include","header");
	    ...
	?>
	    OR
	<?php
	    ...
	    $engine->eTemplate("include","footer");
	    ...
	?>

Notes
   
